<item>
            <title>[LU-434] The $SHARED_DIRECTORY variable could benefit from comments</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-434</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the usage of the $SHARED_DIRECTORY variable was asked about on the Lustre mailing list, it is apparent that it&apos;s intended usage is not entirely clear. Thus, some comments could be added to the code to try and clear up this ambiguity.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The lustre mailing list thread reference above is here: &lt;a href=&quot;http://lists.lustre.org/pipermail/lustre-discuss/2011-June/015681.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://lists.lustre.org/pipermail/lustre-discuss/2011-June/015681.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
